1.0.0.name: wordpress/inboundwriter
1.0.0.description:
Create more engaging and search engine-friendly blog posts directly within the world’s most popular blogging software!

What You Get

With the InboundWriter plugin, writers and bloggers get real-time SEO intelligence streamed directly into their WordPress editor. See what words and phrases your target audience is searching for and sharing online, and how well those words rank on the search engines.

InboundWriter goes beyond traditional SEO by providing real-time scoring and automated guidance and recommendations on how to best structure your posts for maximum online search engine visibility or which terms are most valuable from an advertising perspective. Just follow the steps to create blog posts that deliver a significant increase in search engine traffic or your potential Google AdSense payout.

How Does It Work?

  • Just provide InboundWriter with a starting phrase that relates
